"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-why-runners-wear-arm-sleeves-paris-olympics-b1174820.html\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the search feature\", \"from\": 7, \"to\": 25}, {\"ngram\": \"your consent\", \"from\": 35, \"to\": 47}, {\"ngram\": \"cookies\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 99}, {\"ngram\": \"similar technologies\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"search\", \"from\": 175, \"to\": 181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our privacy policy\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 205}, {\"ngram\": \"more information\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics Over the weekend, the track and field events began at the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sport|Olympics\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 243}, {\"ngram\": \"the weekend\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 260}, {\"ngram\": \"the track and field events\", \"from\": 262, \"to\": 288}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the most popular events of the Games, theathleticsactionhas included a dramatic men's 100m final whenNoah Lyles came from behind to pip Kishane Thompsonby five thousandths of a second and take gold for USA.\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 533, \"end\": 536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999998809762545, \"rank\": 6.626295973443076e-08, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most popular events\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 354}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 367}, {\"ngram\": \"theathleticsactionhas\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 390}, {\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 442}, {\"ngram\": \"pip Kishane Thompsonby\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 485}, {\"ngram\": \"five thousandths\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 502}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The women's 100m final was equally as exciting.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Julien Alfred, the 23-year-old St Lucian,powered away from Sha'Carri Richardson to claim gold- and win the first ever Olympic medal for the Caribbean nation.\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucian\", \"score\": 0.9798768061948612, \"rank\": 0.02053636760892891, \"text\": \"Lucian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucian\"}, {\"begin\": 646, \"end\": 666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sha'Carri Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Julien Alfred\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 600}, {\"ngram\": \"the first ever Olympic medal\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 718}, {\"ngram\": \"the Caribbean nation\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Viewers of the weekend's events might have spotted that some of the athletes competing inrunningwere wearing arm sleeves.\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 867, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Viewers\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 753}, {\"ngram\": \"the weekend's events\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 822}, {\"ngram\": \"arm sleeves\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While they undoubtedly add a splash of style to any running outfit, arm sleeves offer much more than just aesthetic appeal.\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a splash\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"style\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 913}, {\"ngram\": \"any running outfit\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"arm sleeves\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"just aesthetic appeal\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These accessories have gained popularity among athletes for a range of practical benefits, from performance enhancement to recovery support.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These accessories\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1010}, {\"ngram\": \"popularity\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"a range\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"practical benefits\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"performance enhancement\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1112}, {\"ngram\": \"recovery support\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's everything you need to know.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the main reasons some runners opt for arm sleeves is to protect their skin from the sun's harmful ultraviolet (UV) rays.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the main reasons\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"some runners\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"arm sleeves\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"their skin\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1252}, {\"ngram\": \"UV\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While sunscreen can be effective, it often needs reapplication during longer distance runs, and can be uncomfortable when mixed with sweat.\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1438, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sunscreen\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1314}, {\"ngram\": \"reapplication\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1361}, {\"ngram\": \"longer distance runs\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"sweat\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Arm sleeves made with UV-resistant materials provide consistent protection without the need for reapplication, allowing runners to focus on their performance rather than worrying about sunburn or long-term skin damage.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1658, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Arm sleeves\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"UV-resistant materials\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1484}, {\"ngram\": \"consistent protection\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1531}, {\"ngram\": \"reapplication\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1549}, {\"ngram\": \"runners\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"their performance\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"sunburn\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1632}, {\"ngram\": \"long-term skin damage\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Olympians, compression technology is probably the main reason for the popularity of arm sleeves.\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1673}, {\"ngram\": \"compression technology\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1697}, {\"ngram\": \"the main reason\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1725}, {\"ngram\": \"the popularity\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"arm sleeves\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The snug fit of compression sleeves applies gentle pressure to the muscles in the arms, which can enhance circulation and increase oxygen delivery to the muscles.\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1923, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The snug fit\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"compression sleeves\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1796}, {\"ngram\": \"gentle pressure\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"the muscles\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1835}, {\"ngram\": \"the arms\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"circulation\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1878}, {\"ngram\": \"oxygen delivery\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"the muscles\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This improved blood flow can lead to better performance and reduced muscle fatigue.\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 2008, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"better performance\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1980}, {\"ngram\": \"reduced muscle fatigue\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 2007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Compression can also aid in recovery by decreasing the buildup of lactic acid and minimising muscle soreness after a run.\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2130, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Compression\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"recovery\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2045}, {\"ngram\": \"the buildup\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2071}, {\"ngram\": \"lactic acid\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2086}, {\"ngram\": \"muscle soreness\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2117}, {\"ngram\": \"a run\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Arm sleeves can also play an important role in temperature regulation, making them suitable for both hot and cold conditions.\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2257, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Arm sleeves\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"an important role\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2175}, {\"ngram\": \"temperature regulation\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"both hot and cold conditions\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In cooler weather, the sleeves act as an additional layer that helps retain body heat, keeping muscles warm and reducing the risk of injury.\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2398, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cooler weather\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2275}, {\"ngram\": \"the sleeves\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2288}, {\"ngram\": \"an additional layer\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"body heat\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2343}, {\"ngram\": \"muscles\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBA London 2026 LIVE: Memphis Grizzlies vs Orlando Magic come to the UK Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year Winter escapes and activities to end the year in style Conversely, in warmer climates, specially designed sleeves made from moisture-wicking fabrics can help keep runners cool by drawing sweat away from the skin and allowing it to evaporate more efficiently.\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2400, \"end\": 2403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999999714277696, \"rank\": 2.8274390091498422e-08, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2404, \"end\":